This is a placeholder for the actual binary pickle file.
The file camb_grid.pkl will be generated by running code/analysis/generate_grid.py
and will contain the pre-computed CAMB likelihood grid.

Structure of the pickle file:
{
    'parameters': {
        'H0': np.ndarray,
        'Omega_m': np.ndarray,
        'ns': np.ndarray,
        'tau': np.ndarray
    },
    'l_values': np.ndarray,
    'likelihoods': np.ndarray (4D array),
    'spectra': np.ndarray (5D array),
    'metadata': dict
}

To generate this file, run:
python code/analysis/generate_grid.py
